HEADWORD: aneurin
<hw>aneurin</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>Same as <er>thiamin</er>; a B
vitamin (vitamin B1) that prevents beriberi.</def> <altsp>[Also spelled
<asp>aneurine</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> vitamin B1, thiamin, antiberiberi factor</syn>⟦br⟧
